data.description: Spectacular Move In Amazing! This recently renovated 4 bedroom bi-level with finished lower level on (almost) half acre lot. Fleetwood Schools.  Main floor... gray luxury plank floors,  pellet stove), dining room (with ceiling fan), kitchen with renovated cabinets, gorgeous new quartz countertops and even on the island, double sink and appliances and a full bath with 3 private bedrooms. Lower level is finished to provide master bedroom with brick wood fireplace, tile and tile floors,  full bath  with stall shower.   Outside they have recently put in a large privacy vinyl fencing. You have 2 sheds (one large enough to fit all types of equipment even a car) next to the driveway and a large one inside the fenced in yard. The large deck newly painted and swing set/play house. This owner shows such pride in ownership with all that they have recently had done to this home! Fall in love and make this home your home. Please give us a call for your showings before this one is gone. A one year home warranty with an acceptable offer too!
